{"tid":2136941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《半澤直樹2》台灣國旗被消失","createTime":"2020-08-02T13:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T13:57:20.000Z","uid":291252,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a062c2b70acd7611df1dcc0858512c23dc6af331","tid":2136941,"uid":291252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:42:24.000Z","msg":"垃圾豚局已跪 奶泡菜奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睽違7年的神劇《半澤直樹2》終於在本月19日於日本TBS電視台開播，除了收視率同樣創下佳績，《半》劇標籤（＃半沢直樹）更是連兩周登上世界推特趨勢冠軍。也因為本劇太受歡迎，TBS還在本周日（26日）下午、播出第2集前，重播第1集。不過，網友們赫然發現，原本第1集中出現在半澤直樹辦公桌後面，顯示全球23個股市升跌幅電子螢幕上的各國國旗，在重播及第2集中，竟突然全部「消失」。外界推測，可能是台灣（中華民國）國旗出現在螢幕正中央，震碎中國網友的玻璃心，引發向TBS群起抗議。《哈芬頓郵報》（Huffington Post）日文版報導，就此事向TBS查證，TBS昨天做出回答，指刪除理由「無可奉告」。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200729/5LPZOZQ3G753KTGWVGCTUDBONI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200729%2F5LPZOZQ3G753KTGWVGCTUDBONI%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAneaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=2520022e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200729%2F5LPZOZQ3G753KTGWVGCTUDBONI%2F&h=17f2e593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200729/5LPZOZQ3G753KTGWVGCTUDBONI/</a>"},{"pid":"fc9896acc3c4b09c8d13a7e3c456dddbf4d35625","tid":2136941,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔：我睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fdafed9080e276b9d938b677e45adbce6051e8","tid":2136941,"uid":291252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc9896acc3c4b09c8d13a7e3c456dddbf4d35625","tid":2136941,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:43:43.000Z","msg":"連登仔：我睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"唔係仲睇阿嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog